{"tid":1435197,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[出左Twitter] 香港警察用懷疑橡膠彈直接射中BBC 記者頭部","createTime":"2019-08-09T03:37:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T09:54:27.000Z","uid":22556,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9dc6027e0057d07a835b75e9d234b98f886bef09","tid":1435197,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:37:33.000Z","msg":"【警察向BBC駐港記者頭部射擊！】<br />\n<br />\n舉晒手表露身份都係咁，香港要多謝警隊<br />\n<br />\n响8月5號，BBC駐香港記者Stephen McDonell（即係識駐中國多年中文嗰個），响自己個Twitter表示自己比香港警察，近距離（20m內）用射擊（projectile fired ），射爆咗個面罩。佢當日緊係想繼續出tweet講解事發經過啦，但係未開始講就有簡體人問佢死得未。佢立即回應tag埋中國《環球時報》主編胡生，問要唔要轉載件事。終於明白點解要多謝同支持警察喇，可能就係佢地同啲簡體字兵團，令外國記者越黎越有立場。<br />\n<br />\n之後佢當然繼續狂出tweet，先執住支催淚彈，問香港警察有無睇instructions寫住&rdquo;Do not fire directly at persons&rdquo;（不可直接向人發射）。繼而再影懷疑射中佢個面罩嘅橡膠子彈，多謝間防毒面罩公司話&rdquo;make the mask strong&rdquo; （玩Trump Trump嘅金句？！）。佢話當時啲香港防暴警察，用水平角度&rdquo;horizontally&rdquo;唔多過20米向佢發射。之後就話警方話兩個月黎射咗成千粒催淚彈，不過剩係當日（5號）就射咗800粒。<br />\n<br />\n好喇到戲肉，佢形容自己當時同示威者被迫到响路中心，佢同示威者唔同係著藍色衫，著住寫有&quot;MEDIA&rdquo;嘅背心，頭盔亦係藍色（唔係示威者嘅黃色）。對住警察嘅時候，雙手舉高不停做&rdquo;media&rdquo;（我係記者）嘅手勢。結果就被近距離射擊中面部，防毒面罩即時爆咗。因為中咗嘢之後見唔到有煙，所以佢覺得係橡膠子彈多過係催淚彈。最後佢話自己唔應該同攝影師走散，不過多謝其它記者傳媒幫手。<br />\n<br />\n坦白講，以一個咁資深嘅BBC記者嘅Tweet，其實佢寫得出奇地雜亂（太長太多自己睇），可以想象到佢當時嘅感受。當對待記者都尚且如此，大家諗下啲「前線」年青人有咩感覺？無論咩立場嘅香港人，請不要再問點解外國傳媒咁「偏幫」示威者，要問就問警察叔叔。<br />\n<br />\nPhoto Source: Stephen McDonell Twitter<br />\n原Tweet傳送門：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/stephenmcdonell/status/1158315599346335746?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstephenmcdonell%2Fstatus%2F1158315599346335746%3Fs%3D21&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzVxDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=e679e4de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fstephenmcdonell%2Fstatus%2F1158315599346335746%3Fs%3D21&h=08b63a18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/stephenmcdonell/status/1158315599346335746?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n#多謝警察宣傳香港<br />\n#TheWorldIsWatching<br />\n#ThePressIsActuallyFeeling<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/153006095227869/posts/602352440293230?s=754475037&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F153006095227869%2Fposts%2F602352440293230%3Fs%3D754475037%26sfns%3Dmo&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzVxDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=a872acf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/153006095227869/posts/602352440293230?s=754475037&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"239915b9bdd7c4edc6c3543b8a05c6317e753151","tid":1435197,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:38:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46187630116c10322fb0855077ff2322e5ff302d","tid":1435197,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:38:39.000Z","msg":"Old news"},{"pid":"fad5a94616a5d2787feb1d62ea840145bf0be754","tid":1435197,"uid":260036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b95c03fb59f1e5831f55441f294dcffde538003a","tid":1435197,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:47:58.000Z","msg":"8.9 機場萬人接機<br />\n開始時間： 2019年8月9日下午1 點起<br />\n地點 ： 一號客運大樓機場接機大堂<br />\n1. 不申請不反對通知書<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 和平靜坐，不衝擊不破壞不入禁區</span><br />\n3. Be water<br />\n4. 促政府答應五大訴求<br />\n5. 停止暴力打壓示威遊行<br />\n少你一個真係少好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日1:00 機場見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/06Qc3tF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F06Qc3tF.png&h=8bf84c52&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e6741939afd0ab64e9851f9d96893222c93a7070","tid":1435197,"uid":108814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:42:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外國勢力呢屌"},{"pid":"572b4878372579c5